Koharia

This product is a derivative work based on Mihon:
https://github.com/mihonapp/mihon

Original upstream work:
- Mihon
- Originally created by Javier Tomas
- Later maintained and extended by Mihon contributors
- Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

Koharia-specific modifications include, among other changes:
- Renaming and rebranding the application and package identifiers
- Adapting the application into an independent third-party client focused on Komga server browsing and reading
- Reworking download behavior for Komga offline caching and raw-file downloads
- Updating documentation, repository metadata, and project descriptions for derivative-work compliance

Koharia is an independent third-party project and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or maintained by the Mihon project or the Komga project.

Names of upstream projects are used in this repository only to identify origin, compatibility, or attribution where required.
